{"tid":363100,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟古人識唔識得econ？","createTime":"2017-08-17T11:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T16:54:52.000Z","uid":81190,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01450fcf53f9e68e6c4aba61ac37144f966fe99e","tid":363100,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:37:41.000Z","msg":"今時今日，每個國家都有個財政部長，同埋央行行長睇住國家嘅錢，市場動態。<br />\n但係喺古代，尤其是中國，有冇一個類似今日財政部長或者央行行長嘅角色睇住啲錢，控制貨幣數量嘅呢"},{"pid":"ec80e7ff8a9504137a561f91fe70107abe3888c4","tid":363100,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:57:19.000Z","msg":"近排先買左本書講呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫The Reckoning: Financial Accountability and the Rise and Fall of Nations"},{"pid":"96a54800e48087722164126fd1ba65200c644c88","tid":363100,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T11:58:13.000Z","msg":"之前都買左本中華書局出版嘅<br />\n叫早期經濟思想<br />\n講adam Smith之前嘅經濟"},{"pid":"dd587a269eb1614edf7c0c77e9cced6735a80b65","tid":363100,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近排先買左本書講呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫The Reckoning: Financial Accountability and the Rise and Fall of Nations</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3187c001149ae109ed61ed85667b30098cf23735","tid":363100,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:49:10.000Z","msg":"古時有戶部"},{"pid":"ff7cea63083ed828183f5b4514924f99e9a2da5a","tid":363100,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:17:36.000Z","msg":"econ嚟講宋朝算係數一數二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發明左好多金融、經濟概念"},{"pid":"89c60b1f68e4794dadd23ade9c25452864d5eeba","tid":363100,"uid":17335,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:19:35.000Z","msg":"荀子經濟學，足國之道&mdash;&mdash;富國篇<br />\n<a href=\"http://deliver90.blogspot.tw/2017/04/ep22.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdeliver90.blogspot.tw%2F2017%2F04%2Fep22.html&d=963wBI5SM1HAvGOLyy79mUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=330fab33\" target=\"_blank\">http://deliver90.blogspot.tw/2017/04/ep22.html</a>"},{"pid":"7cf7dff015ea4aca6e11d70877a40df9a631a102","tid":363100,"uid":44297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:20:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>econ嚟講宋朝算係數一數二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發明左好多金融、經濟概念</blockquote><br />\n交子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9ed5cde7b4106642d07f63429a2043284c21de","tid":363100,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:53:43.000Z","msg":"鹽鐵論算唔算講緊國家干預經濟"},{"pid":"17c879d6b3f0dd35aa7f483ae5fe731cb1e64508","tid":363100,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:56:32.000Z","msg":"其實類似財政部基本上係政府都有<br />\n但央行行長呢類調控金融就應該冇<br />\n其實應該話金融體系未發達到需要都有呢樣野"},{"pid":"b89474d259b52568e2971d16fb54392a186e029d","tid":363100,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:58:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實類似財政部基本上係政府都有<br />\n但央行行長呢類調控金融就應該冇<br />\n其實應該話金融體系未發達到需要都有呢樣野</blockquote><br />\n均輸平準算唔算？"},{"pid":"b5ca22ca9673e66e77ec64406559ada4377b3689","tid":363100,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T01:25:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>econ嚟講宋朝算係數一數二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發明左好多金融、經濟概念</blockquote><br />\n但對比起西方仲係差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n義大利嘅城邦貿易非常繁盛，因此面對住越黎越複雜嘅商業問題，包括股權呢d問題，d商人發明左double entry accouting system去handle成盤生意<br />\n<br />\n係accounting呢方面完勝東方"},{"pid":"a9b1863665bcc91b3a3454acb31ff87b11b4a365","tid":363100,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T01:40:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前都買左本中華書局出版嘅<br />\n叫早期經濟思想<br />\n講adam Smith之前嘅經濟</blockquote><br />\n原來係中世紀個陣就已經有討論，究竟炒樓炒商品係咪合符道德標準(耶教道德)<br />\n<br />\n古希臘時代已經探討緊商人嘅特權，自由港，點保護外地同本地商人權益從而促進商貿呢類問題，有咩貨物係可以進出，有咩唔可以，貨幣(金/銀)可唔可以自由進出<br />\n<br />\n可以話古希臘嘅經濟思想比起今時今日準備鎖國嘅中共更為先進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880ae7614164e8ffcf1bea2da05c54df778bfbe3","tid":363100,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T01:47:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前都買左本中華書局出版嘅<br />\n叫早期經濟思想<br />\n講adam Smith之前嘅經濟</blockquote><br />\n原來係中世紀個陣就已經有討論，究竟炒樓炒商品係咪合符道德標準(耶教道德)<br />\n<br />\n古希臘時代已經探討緊商人嘅特權，自由港，點保護外地同本地商人權益從而促進商貿呢類問題，有咩貨物係可以進出，有咩唔可以，貨幣(金/銀)可唔可以自由進出<br />\n<br />\n可以話古希臘嘅經濟思想比起今時今日準備鎖國嘅中共更為先進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最驚訝係雅典一早有基金/集資呢類concept<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n集資去建立d船隊，從而再係個到賺取利息<br />\n政府建立嘅公共資產(例如:船隊，海員)可以租借畀外國，或者其他商人作私人目的"},{"pid":"babd7b5baf17cfc87bd842661b439ca413afa34c","tid":363100,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T01:54:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>econ嚟講宋朝算係數一數二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發明左好多金融、經濟概念</blockquote><br />\n但對比起西方仲係差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n義大利嘅城邦貿易非常繁盛，因此面對住越黎越複雜嘅商業問題，包括股權呢d問題，d商人發明左double entry accouting system去handle成盤生意<br />\n<br />\n係accounting呢方面完勝東方</blockquote><br />\nDouble entry聽講係修道院發明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8659194cb78ac6268c6f12bae4e5fa4d5f1f9e7c","tid":363100,"uid":126902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T03:02:03.000Z","msg":"鹽鐵論成日聽，佢算唔算"},{"pid":"aafdc5dbf68637a8601329c8dd9713cbdfb09a22","tid":363100,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T04:05:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>econ嚟講宋朝算係數一數二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發明左好多金融、經濟概念</blockquote><br />\n但對比起西方仲係差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n義大利嘅城邦貿易非常繁盛，因此面對住越黎越複雜嘅商業問題，包括股權呢d問題，d商人發明左double entry accouting system去handle成盤生意<br />\n<br />\n係accounting呢方面完勝東方</blockquote><br />\n差幾遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />剩係講紙幣已經落後於宋<br />\ndouble entry accouting system 14世紀先發明，宋一早亡左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有<br />\nHowever, the double-entry accounting method was said to be developed independently earlier in Korea during the&nbsp;Goryeo dynasty&nbsp;(918-1392) when&nbsp;Kaesongwas a center of trade and industry at that time. The&nbsp;Four-element bookkeeping system&nbsp;was said to be originated in the 11th or 12th century.[2][3][4]<br />\n歐洲遠遠落後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115df6ac4ff342ac02e42bdbd611f6a254ca039a","tid":363100,"uid":83130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T13:40:10.000Z","msg":"點會唔識 我就係由古代返黎"},{"pid":"1e631a386e627981c01b531b5842a18e2f4a0a11","tid":363100,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:05:05.000Z","msg":"晁錯，鹽鐵輪"},{"pid":"cd05dae8aa84e98e1738903a3c1c055155cd6b53","tid":363100,"uid":26071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:54:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>econ嚟講宋朝算係數一數二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發明左好多金融、經濟概念</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n低稅率 鼓勵自由市場<br />\n疆域細慳翻唔少軍費<br />\n其實國土洗乜要咁大<br />\n只要霸住d具生產力既地方就夠"}]}